result.name: Ippudo

reviews.text: Great food. Tasty. Great quality, good service.

I went there early before lunch time the place was empty , ramen and dumpling is extremely good. Portion is little small so you might need to add extra ramen if you are a guy or get 2 orders of dumplings to fill you up.
For Japanese ramen restaurants in HK, this is definitely above average with reasonable prices.
Spicy ramen was super hot even with the medium degree. So beware!
Staff is very nice, food is very good ! Not expensive, good address.
